Feels great to finally start drawing again :D I figured since #inktober is starting soon I'd do a little warmup. .
So I'm new to the borderlands fandom and I wanted to redesign some of my favs, starting with zero. I find his dry sense of humor to be really funny and I really like those types of characters in general. This design is kinda like an upgraded suit, I tried to make it look like something he'd probably wear and I introduced the tan/cream color to give it more of a "veteran" type of vibe. .
For this year's inktober challenge I'm planning on making an original character based on the word for that day, I'm really looking forward to sharing the results!!!
